fifty-four is a 54lines.com compliance checker.

usage: fifty-four [ file ]
    
    if argv1 is not passed, fifty-four will read from stdin

Exit Codes:
      0) success
     54) file exceeds 54 lines 
     80) some line exceeds 80 characters
    100) improper usage
    111) temporary failure (typically argv 1 is not a file)

Dependencies:
    + Bourne Shell (/bin/sh)
    + awk
